cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment identification, which are common topics in the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of machine learning algorithms and experimentation with various models also suggests the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on accuracy and analysis of misclassified snippets indicates the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
